# Git commits

Never add **any** `Co-authored-by:` line or other trailer footers (`git commit --trailer …`). Never attribute tools, bots, or co-authors in the commit message unless the human author adds that text themselves.

The repo `.githooks/commit-msg` strips `Co-authored-by:` lines; after clone run: `git config core.hooksPath .githooks`
